-- Plinko Labs
--
-- A tiny 3x5 bitmap font so canvases can draw text - scores, labels, HUDs - without any external
-- asset. Each glyph is five 3-wide rows of '#'/'.'; `draw` walks them and calls a `plot(x, y)`
